OL,3,COctopus boss: Energy firms should give
OL,4,Ccash to people losing winter fuel
OL,5,Cpayment
OL,7,FThe boss of Octopus Energy has said
OL,8,Fenergy suppliers should "be helpful"
OL,9,Fto the Government and give extra
OL,10,Fsupport to elderly people losing their
OL,11,Fwinter fuel payments.
OL,13,FGreg Jackson, who founded Octopus in
OL,14,F2016, told PA news agency: "We all
OL,15,Fknow there were some people receiving
OL,16,Fthe winter fuel allowance who didn't
OL,17,Fneed it ` that costs everyone else
OL,18,Fmoney."
