OL,7,FHe added: "But then there's the grey
OL,8,Farea of people losing it that need it
OL,9,F` that's where we can help."
OL,11,FUnder plans announced by Chancellor
OL,12,FRachel Reeves in July, winter fuel
OL,13,Fpayments will be restricted to those
OL,14,Freceiving pension credit.
OL,16,FIt means around 10 million people will
OL,17,Flose out this winter, with the benefit
OL,18,Ftaken away from all but the poorest
OL,19,Fpensioners in the country. About 11.5
OL,20,Fmillion people used to receive it.
