OL,7,FThe Government argues it is right to
OL,8,Fmeans-test the benefit, worth up to
OL,9,F#300, in order to tackle what it calls
OL,10,Fa "black hole" in the public finances.
OL,12,FBut it has also prompted bitter
OL,13,Foutcry, including from some Labour
OL,14,FMPs, with critics pointing out that
OL,15,Fpension credit only tops up income to
OL,16,F#11,300 a year for individuals,
OL,17,Fmeaning many who do not qualify could
OL,18,Fstill struggle paying bills.
