OL,7,FMr Jackson, who has been vocal in his
OL,8,Fsupport for previous Labour policies,
OL,9,Fsaid: "In these transition periods,
OL,10,Fit's easy for people to kick and
OL,11,Fscream.
OL,13,F"Alternatively, companies and others
OL,14,Fcan say: 'How do we make this work in
OL,15,Fa way that is best for Britain and, in
OL,16,Four case, best for our customers?'"
