OL,7,FHe added that the Government has got
OL,8,Fto "make difficult decisions. So now
OL,9,Flet's be helpful in making sure that
OL,10,Fwhen you make those decisions, we can
OL,11,Flook after the people who will be
OL,12,Fworst affected".
OL,14,FHowever, ministers should keep a
OL,15,F"close eye on the impact" of the
OL,16,Fpolicy if this winter is colder than
OL,17,Fusual, Mr Jackson said, and be "ready
OL,18,Fto act" if more support is needed.
