OL,3,COctopus boss: Energy firms should give
OL,4,Ccash to people losing winter fuel
OL,5,Cpayment
OL,7,FOctopus, the UK's largest energy
OL,8,Fsupplier, announced last month that it
OL,9,Fwill continue its #30 million
OL,10,Fassistance fund into this winter for
OL,11,Fpensioners who do not qualify for
OL,12,Fstate support.
OL,14,FThe company also has a range of other
OL,15,Fmeasures, including giving out free
OL,16,Felectric blankets to vulnerable
OL,17,Fcustomers.
