OL,4,Ccash to people losing winter fuel
OL,5,Cpayment
OL,7,FNonetheless, energy suppliers have
OL,8,Fcome under pressure for making large
OL,9,Fprofits over the last two years, while
OL,10,Fbills have rocketed as a result of
OL,11,Fsoaring gas prices.
OL,13,FOctopus turned its first ever profit
OL,14,Fof #203 million for the year ending
OL,15,FApril 2023, the most recent year on
OL,16,Frecord, while revenue tripled to #13
OL,17,Fbillion.
OL,19,FThe company's UK energy retail arm
OL,20,Ftook on #69 million of costs to lower
OL,21,Fcustomer bills over the same period.
