OL,7,FMr Jackson's comments come weeks
OL,8,Fbefore energy bills are due to get
OL,9,Fmore expensive again this winter.
OL,11,FRegulator Ofgem said the average
OL,12,Fhousehold bill is set to increase by
OL,13,F#149 from October after it increased
OL,14,Fthe quarterly price cap for the winter
OL,15,Fmonths.
