OL,7,FLast month, Labour's energy consumers
OL,8,Fminister Miatta Fahnbulleh held talks
OL,9,Fwith suppliers including Octopus,
OL,10,Fasking for help with a marketing
OL,11,Fcampaign to alert customers to bills
OL,12,Fsupport that is already available.
OL,14,FSources with knowledge of the matter
OL,15,Fsaid ministers also asked firms about
OL,16,Flonger term market reforms for energy
OL,17,Fbills, including a social tariff,
OL,18,Fsomething campaign groups have
OL,19,Fproposed for several years.
