OL,5,Cpayment
OL,7,FThe measure would likely take the form
OL,8,Fof a targeted discount energy deal for
OL,9,Fpoorer customers, and could be below
OL,10,Fthe price of the cheapest available
OL,11,Fstandard energy tariff.
OL,13,FMr Jackson said it is "important" to
OL,14,Fbring energy costs down for everyone,
OL,15,Fbut added that "the question is who
OL,16,Fpays" for a social tariff.
