OL,4,Ccash to people losing winter fuel
OL,5,Cpayment
OL,7,FThe system, known as locational
OL,8,Fmarginal pricing, would see people
OL,9,Fliving near wind farms pay less for
OL,10,Felectricity.
OL,12,FRegional pricing is "the critical
OL,13,Fthing we need to do", Mr Jackson said,
OL,14,Fciting a recent report carried out by
OL,15,FFTI Consulting, which claimed it could
OL,16,Fsave bill payers #51 billion by 2040.
OL,18,FOctopus already offers time-specific
OL,19,Fdiscounts for people living near wind
OL,20,Ffarms of up to 50% in high winds, when
OL,21,Fthe turbines generate more power.
