OL,7,FMr Jackson said that while the biggest
OL,8,Fdiscounts "will be the areas with the
OL,9,Fmost electricity generation", such as
OL,10,Fareas of Scotland, the price would
OL,11,Fdrop "in every region" because the
OL,12,Ftransmission system would also be
OL,13,F"more efficient".
OL,15,FThe Labour Government has introduced a
OL,16,Fswathe of changes since the general
OL,17,Felection, including forming a new
OL,18,Fstate energy investment firm, GB
OL,19,FEnergy, to help boost renewables in
OL,20,Frecent months.
